graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Operator]

    %% External Required Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|coordinates metadata| etcd[etcd 3.x<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|manages resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Optional Dependencies - Storage
    ModelMesh -.->|model artifacts| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|model artifacts| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>OPTIONAL alternative]

    %% External Optional Dependencies - Model Runtimes (one of many)
    subgraph "Model Server Runtimes (Choose One or More)"
        Triton[Triton Inference Server 2.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
        MLServer[MLServer 1.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
        OVMS[OpenVINO Model Server 1.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
        TorchServe[TorchServe 0.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    end
    ModelMesh -.->|runtime option 1| Triton
    ModelMesh -.->|runtime option 2| MLServer
    ModelMesh -.->|runtime option 3| OVMS
    ModelMesh -.->|runtime option 4| TorchServe

    %% External Optional Dependencies - Infrastructure
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ModelMesh -.->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics scraping| Monitoring[Monitoring<br/>ServiceMonitor<br/>INTERNAL]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|manages via API| ModelMesh
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| ModelMesh

    %% Network dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|watches CRDs| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|creates deployments| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|model coordination| etcd

    %% CRD compatibility
    KServe[KServe API<br/>Compatibility] -.->|InferenceService CR| ModelMesh

    %% Styling
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style etcd fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style PVC fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Triton fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style MLServer fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OVMS fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style TorchServe fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KServe fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Legend
    classDef required fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    classDef optional fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef internal fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    classDef integration fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
